description: "Chart of the Sunda Strait, focusing on bays and islands, and showing bathymetry (sea depth), anchor points, shoals and reefs, landmarks, and a rhumbline network, all to aid navigation. Includes an inset map of the bay of the city of Banten on Java."
title: "Straat Sunda in de Oost-Indische Zee tussen de Eylanden Sumatra en Java"
